*** What is PyOpenAL?

This is the port for Python of the OpenAL library.


*** Requirement

 * Python

 * Linux (any architecture; other OS may be supported but have not
   been tested at all)

 * OpenAL


*** Installation

Follow the sequence:

$ python setup.py build
$ su   # enter the root password
$ python setup.py install


